      "filePath": "PunchPressVision/infrastructure/ControlModule/include/infrastructure/ControlModule/ControlModule.hpp",
      "summary": "PLC 控制网关头文件，声明 ControlModule 类（继承 QObject 和 global::IInfrastructure），封装 Modbus TCP 通信：连接管理、保持寄存器读写（含浮点拆分）、批量寄存器操作、线圈读写，并通过 connectionStateChanged 信号通知连接状态。",
      "tags": ["api-handler", "modbus", "plc", "hardware-abstraction", "header"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "使用 Q_OBJECT 宏支持 Qt 信号槽机制；寄存器地址映射引用 ConfigModule::plcAddressCfg"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:PunchPressVision/infrastructure/ControlModule/src/ControlModule.cpp",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "ControlModule.cpp",
      "filePath": "PunchPressVision/infrastructure/ControlModule/src/ControlModule.cpp",
      "summary": "ControlModule 的完整实现：基于 rw::hoep::ModbusDevice 实现 Modbus TCP 连接/断开、保持寄存器读写（单字/浮点/批量）、线圈读写；所有操作均做空指针检查和异常捕获，连接状态通过 atomic_bool 线程安全维护并发射 Qt 信号。",
      "tags": ["api-handler", "modbus", "plc", "hardware-abstraction", "implementation"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "大端字节序（BigEndian）用于浮点寄存器编解码；使用 std::atomic_bool 配合 memory_order_release/acquire 确保线程安全"
    },
